yTime":"2018-06-04T06:08:52.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>「抗爭者支援基金」，今日將會在銅鑼灣前往維園方向，設立籌款街站，為基金籌款。</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n呢個基金勁仆街, 應該係人都知！<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">另外，係維園外設街立籌款, 唔駛上繳10%比支聯會！</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"07b9119c40f14f14ae55a4e9e912e7e7c1561d14","tid":689362,"uid":79563,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9dcd5fa90f6535dbde58199ae3a31cb11f4a2492","tid":689362,"uid":35136,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"88b9ea4b0e76e263ab8ff8547f3519555ae88e82","tid":689362,"uid":134071,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2018-06-04T04:26:03.000Z","msg":"現任學聯主席偉論<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://bkb.mpweekly.com/cu0001/20180601-75896\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fbkb.mpweekly.com%2Fcu0001%2F20180601-75896&d=xViEvuVumwDc6BNzy5dOxzA5unq%2FSd9ZKvr75NUD1%2F0%3D&h=cc13b991\" target=\"_blank\">http://bkb.mpweekly.com/cu0001/20180601-75896</a><br />\n<br />\n陶：陶君行（一九八九年學聯秘書長）<br />\n張：張倩盈（本屆學聯代表會主席）<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n張：我本身有讀國際政治，用現實主義少少去看，<strong>中國是否適合有民主政制，其實未有結論，所以不會說中國一定有民主對全世界是好。</strong><br />\n<br />\n陶：那香港又怎樣？<br />\n<br />\n張：<strong>我認為香港應該要有民主</strong>。如果有一個scenario（情形），是香港有民主，而中國仍是沒辦法有民主，都是我們的其中一個目標。<br />\n<br />\n陶：中國一日無民主，又點會接受到香港有民主？<br />\n<br />\n<strong>張：這個機會是存在的，假設用香港獨立或其他方式。</strong><br />\n<br />\n陶：中國一日無民主，點會讓香港獨立？雨傘運動就是一個實戰經驗，一天中國未有民主，是不能容讓你有民主，何況獨立？<br />\n<br />\n張：我覺得你對形勢的判斷只屬於這一刻。我不是說自己想法，常聽到香港後生仔有好多想像，例如常常拿來說笑的「支爆」（中國經濟爆破或崩潰），或者政權的變化。因為我們覺得民主中國已經不是一個我要去爭取的目標，中國民主就好像一個夢想一樣，如果是（民主）當然好，但遙不可及。"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-04T04:59:20.000Z","msg":"中國一日無民主，又點會接受到中國有民主?"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-04T06:10:27.000Z","msg":"「中國一日無民主，點會讓香港獨立？」<br />\n<br />\n笑死人咩！從來無支那民運人士承諾保證過, 支那有民主, 香港就可以獨立<br />\n<br />\n既然係咁, 我香港仲乜事要幫支那國有民主?"},{"pid":"3488e07f96f91800a42a32121e0be61a458b982c","tid":689362,"uid":24140,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"6e743f12c85eb50e09087d86936ab9c630870c54","tid":689362,"uid":51469,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"a8e5268c765a03ffd52f644aaf26b1a5b0f08340","tid":689362,"uid":24140,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"c67d951a8f3bdb3d96fa96e2eb4b8d13ca724e99","tid":689362,"uid":134071,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-04T06:03:47.000Z","msg":"廢陶係廢係人都知<br />\n<br />\n但今次學聯&quot;不出席六四晚會, 但會在場外籌款&quot;真係好笑<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-04T06:07:21.000Z","msg":"佢地迫於現實要低頭無辦法<br />\n<br />\n廢陶廢唔廢就後話<br />\n但呢段野硬係覺得有問題<br />\n但講唔出係邊到有問題 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n感覺佢搞錯左蘇聯收皮既原因"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-04T06:08:18.000Z","msg":"現實低頭<br />\n嘩<br />\n講得好好聽喎<br />\n一早唔知要低頭?"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-04T06:12:28.000Z","msg":"佢地唔會低頭低到無哂底線LO <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e350a0ebf29eb87d511c4ebb9bd6b4e047e5d45c","tid":689362,"uid":142903,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-04T06:13:24.000Z","msg":"Cheap過雞"},{"pid":"151d5d6cd8eba34fa5cc109b590f63770b9a4d64","tid":689362,"uid":28503,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-04T06:14:00.000Z","msg":"完美演繹政棍兩個字<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6632b26303fc1666cd12f325dacda155e8bd9c26","tid":689362,"uid":51469,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"3488e07f96f91800a42a32121e0be61a458b982c","tid":689362,"uid":24140,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quot