Time":"2018-06-04T06:02:10.000Z","msg":"張：因為有戈爾巴喬夫的出現。<br />\n<br />\n陶：你都要做些東西，facilitate（促使）到戈爾巴喬夫的出現。你想靠支爆，你想靠美國佬，你都要製造一個土壤出來讓人們支持我們，內地我們都要facilitate到一個土壤讓戈爾巴喬夫出來搞黨內改革。無這樣的推力去爭取中國民主，又怎會有黨外不同意見人士肯走出來話爭取民主，這是我的point。我知是遙不可及好困難，但是世事若被我們估到，我們就好好啦。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n無人覺得廢陶個講法有問題? <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-04T06:18:19.000Z","msg":"戈<span style=\"color: red;\">爾</span>巴喬夫<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"76a3eb89294cc75284c0c6992cb59dfd562b7652","tid":689362,"uid":26156,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-04T06:21:53.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"43d0ab9744bf2279a99e7a35497c25f6c964ed62","tid":689362,"uid":26156,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-04T06:22:06.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"b9b82f45826fb2a3cba93810dea27f6e9b1b37c8","tid":689362,"uid":24140,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e8050f1867ce6e1c553c4c67e14b9564442a1c59","tid":689362,"uid":51469,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-04T06:17:02.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>佢地迫於現實要低頭無辦法<br />\n<br />\n廢陶廢唔廢就後話<br />\n但呢段野硬係覺得有問題<br />\n但講唔出係邊到有問題 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n感覺佢搞錯左蘇聯收皮既原因</blockquote>現實低頭<br />\n嘩<br />\n講得好好聽喎<br />\n一早唔知要低頭?</blockquote>佢地唔會低頭低到無哂底線LO <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote>唔去人地集會<br />\n去人地場外籌款<br />\n呢條底線都好高下喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote>"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-04T06:24:16.000Z","msg":"佢地講明支援抗爭者不分派別<br />\n<br />\n另一邊呢?"},{"pid":"b10d3786025da5dbbfab42a94766aef552c31a9c","tid":689362,"uid":62809,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-04T06